These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, light-blue, blue, green, orange, brown
7 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, chinchilla, lizard, frog, cat, ferret
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the owner of the cat##2
 9. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes green##1
12. the person who likes green is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
14. the owner of the cat is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
16. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
18. the person who likes brown is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | lilac  | orange        | green | light-blue      | blue     | turquise      | brown     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | lizard         | ferret   | horse | cat    | frog | chinchilla |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

