 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the fan of disco is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person eating strawberry and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
15. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
16. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
